Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.47,0:00:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0090,,{\fad(400,400)\fs36\fnMSungHK-Bold\bord0\shad2}2024年10月24日 第55層·格朗薩姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.15,0:00:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況我已經瞭解了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.16,0:00:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會向眾團員解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.30,0:00:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我們要申請暫時退團
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由是?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們對血盟騎士團的現狀抱有疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.67,0:00:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信你們很快就會重返戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.17,0:00:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0090,,{\fad(400,400)\fs36\fnMSungHK-Bold\bord0\shad2}2024年10月25日 第22層
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.24,0:00:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風景不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.66,0:00:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不要太接近外圍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:00:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買了套好房子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.35,0:01:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我也因此身無分文了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.49,0:01:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在這裡就能過上平靜的生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.74,0:01:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.90,0:01:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.35,0:01:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們之間的關係僅存在於這個世界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.73,0:01:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要生氣了 桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.93,0:01:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這裡是假想世界 我的心意也是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡學會了一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.71,0:01:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是永不言棄並堅持到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.93,0:01:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是回到了原來的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會再次和桐人相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.98,0:01:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再次愛上你

Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.34,0:02:08.70,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}認めてた臆病な過去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:16.77,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}分からないままに怖がってた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.14,0:02:18.89,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}後ろの自分が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:25.72,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}現実を今に映す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:30.83,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}いくつもの空を描いた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:32.89,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}ここはきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:38.37,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}儚い心 乱して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:44.08,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}夢で高く飛んだ躰は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.15,0:02:46.94,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}どんな不安纏っても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:48.98,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}振り払ってく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:53.42,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}眠る小さな想い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:55.64,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}広がりだして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:57.70,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}気づく 弱い 私
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:03:04.40,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}君がいれば 暗い世界 強くいれた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:10.16,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}長い夢見る心は そう 永遠で
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.77,0:03:14.27,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}I wanna always stay with you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:19.87,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}I give you everything I have

Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.34,0:02:08.70,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}正視著膽怯的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:16.77,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}依然無法理解地畏懼著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.14,0:02:18.89,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}背後的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:25.72,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}此刻映照在現實中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:30.83,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}描繪了數片天空的此處
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:32.89,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}一定是在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:38.37,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}亂我脆弱心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:44.08,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}乘著夢想高飛身軀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.15,0:02:46.94,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}無論有任何不安糾纏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:48.98,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}都掙脫前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:53.42,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}將沉睡著的小小的心願
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:55.64,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}擴展開來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:57.70,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}意識到弱小的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:03:04.40,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}只要有你在 黑暗的世界 也能一直堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:10.16,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}用沉眠許久的心 永遠堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.77,0:03:14.27,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}I wanna always stay with you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:19.87,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}I give you everything I have

