Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝露少女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看他平時傲慢不羈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到還有著天真 或者說是說孩子氣的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會年齡比我小吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽到我剛才的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的話是指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 今天要去哪裡玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.77,0:04:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天 前天 還有前段日子已經玩得夠多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 桐人不想出去玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.43,0:04:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道一個應該很有趣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.37,0:05:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是 我們要去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去到那裡自然會有驚喜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.73,0:05:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 讓我騎脖子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.19,0:05:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騎…騎脖子?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為一直從同一高度看風景太無趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.49,0:05:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以桐人的力量值來說這應該是易如反掌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.43,0:05:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也…也許是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你年齡也不小了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和年齡毫無關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼所謂 又沒有人看著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.66,0:05:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢回頭看我就揍你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這未免太蠻橫了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 從這裡已經能看到湖泊了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.93,0:06:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.54,0:06:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後換我來背你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 開始前進
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前進方向 東北偏北
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.93,0:06:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有人看著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.84,0:06:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是有人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 桐人也揮下手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下來會比較好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我在村裡聽到一個傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一帶的森林的深處會出現那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.62,0:07:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是指鬼魂系的怪物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說那是反覆遭到獵殺的怪物的怨念
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每晚都在野外徘徊著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.71,0:07:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.13,0:07:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳聞中的那個地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大約一週前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有位木工玩家到這裡取木材
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他專心收集木材的時候不覺間已經入夜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而後他就在不遠處的樹蔭下瞥見一白色物體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.14,0:08:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知是怪物還是其他的什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那白色的影子慢步走向樹林的另一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…快放我下來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.42,0:08:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐…桐人 那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.52,0:08:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:08:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:08:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…玩家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.33,0:09:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有光標
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有什麼Bug嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼小的孩子會在SAO裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之不能這麼放著不管
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等她醒來就應該能問個明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先帶她回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先有一點可以確認的是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能像這樣帶回家的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會是NPC吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是NPC的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.89,0:09:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人抱起她的時候就會出現騷擾警告了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這也不是觸發什麼任務的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是的話 任務日誌窗口應該會更新
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.86,0:10:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個孩子終究是玩家 在哪裡迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣想才最為合理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.04,0:10:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 為什麼會在那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.71,0:10:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不清楚箇中的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.50,0:10:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這孩子應該有父母或者監護人什麼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一定是和家人一起登錄的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願他們平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會恢復意識吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的身體還未消失
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明她和NERvGear之間還存在著信號往來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她現在是處於類似睡眠的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以過不了多久她就會醒來的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這個孩子是孤身一人來到SAO這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.48,0:11:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直孤獨地活在這個世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天能醒過來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐…桐人 桐人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你醒來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得在自己身上發生過什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字呢 說得出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名…名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.36,0:12:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結…衣?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結衣 那就是我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結衣啊 不錯的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.81,0:12:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.94,0:12:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞…娜 木…人?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.34,0:12:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說結衣妹妹 你為什麼會到森林裡去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的父母是在什麼地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.66,0:12:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.52,0:13:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結衣妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以叫你結衣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.19,0:13:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 那結衣也叫我桐人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.81,0:13:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木…人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.76,0:13:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是桐人 桐·人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.86,0:13:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能有點難念
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便用個容易念的叫法就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.14,0:13:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.03,0:13:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞娜是媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.57,0:13:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.15,0:13:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是媽媽啊 小結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.26,0:13:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:13:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.05,0:14:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了吧 我們吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.64,0:14:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 小結衣吃這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結衣 這個非常辣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和爸爸一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.79,0:14:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 既然你有這般覺悟 我就不阻止你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡事都需要經歷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.21,0:14:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:14:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子真有骨氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯就挑戰一下勁辣大餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.21,0:14:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會做那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.51,0:15:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說桐人 你怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.37,0:15:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒有了記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但更重要的是她這樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像變成了嬰兒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.50,0:15:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我不知道該怎麼辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.18,0:15:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想在結衣恢復記憶之前一直照顧她對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是左右為難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不回去攻略遊戲的話 就不能早日將結衣解放
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 就做我們力所能及的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從結衣的裝備看來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:16:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難想像她一直以來長居於野外
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先去起始之鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打聽一下這孩子有沒有父母或兄弟姐妹之類的家人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.27,0:16:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想跟結衣分開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.47,0:16:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間雖短
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.55,0:16:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但自從有了結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就變得像個真正的家一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼覺得的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們也不是再也見不到她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.21,0:16:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且如果這孩子有家人或者監護人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們現在一定很擔心她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等結衣睡醒之後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就到起始之鎮去找找看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們姑且先準備好武器以便能隨時裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟那裡是軍隊的勢力範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心為上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:17:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0090,,{\fad(400,400)\fs36\fnMSungHK-Bold\bord0\shad2}2024年10月31日 第1層·起始之鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久沒到這裡來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.45,0:17:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼建築是你有印象的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.05,0:17:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也難怪 畢竟起始之鎮大得可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先去中央市場看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.64,0:17:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還有多少玩家在這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前SAO裡存活的玩家大約有6000人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括軍隊在內應該約有三成的人還留在起始之鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以應該有將近兩千人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而這裡未免太冷清了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把孩子們還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保姆登場了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久候大駕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把孩子們還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把話說得那麼難聽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不過是教小孩子一些社會常識罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是軍隊的重要使命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 市民們可是負有納稅的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀 凱因 米奈 你們都在那嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗夏老師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 救救我們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用顧慮錢的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把錢全給他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.36,0:18:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 只給這麼一點沒是用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.27,0:18:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們可是拖欠著巨額的稅金啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝備也得留下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括所有防具
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一件不漏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開…你們給我讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了 把裝備都取回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 你們是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.87,0:19:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要妨礙我們執行軍務嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從未見過你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們可否知道與軍隊作對意味著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.66,0:19:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人 照看好結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.77,0:19:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.12,0:20:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在圈內無論受到什麼攻擊HP都不會減少
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 最多只會發生輕微的反衝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.48,0:20:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以相對的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圈內戰鬥會讓人切身體會到恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.27,0:20:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別光在看 快點動手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,0:20:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊 大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.78,0:20:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是第一次看到那樣的招數
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.28,0:20:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真是太帥了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:20:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝您的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 媽媽強得一塌糊塗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.38,0:21:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的心正在…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.15,0:21:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結衣?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小結衣?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.74,0:21:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結衣 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.24,0:21:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結衣?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小結衣 是不是想起什麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.04,0:21:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不曾在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是一個人在漆黑的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結衣…
